title: What Is Affiliate Marketing?
description: What is affiliate marketing? Affiliate marketing is the process of matching up affiliate programs or products with targeted audience. Success of any affiliate marketing campaign depends on the quality of the affiliate product, suitability of the advertising channel to that product and the cost of advertising. Quality low cost traffic will lead to positive ROIs and profit for the affiliate marketer.  Affiliate marketer needs to learn basic knowledge, practice and be patient to become skillful in affiliate marketing and make money online
